title: Behind the Lens: Summer 2013 Volcomunity Creative Liberation
description:
Volcom surfer Quincy Davis shows us the behind the lens sneak peak of her Summer 2013 design capsule collection with Volcom. Shot on location in Long Beach, California Quincy gives us a look into a typical summer day... with one uncommon thing, camera's are filming her every step!

- Music -

Song: "Old Paladino"
Artist: TRMRS
Release: Trmrs Tape : Side B
